metadata.name: Elite Ape Comic: Apes Out on the Town
metadata.description: PUNKS Comic partners with your favorite Bored Apes to release Apes Out on the Town! In their constant pursuit of relieving boredom, a small crew of apes travel to Origin City for a night out on the town. Readers of PUNKS #2 will recognize the familiar faces of Hanzo, Lone Star, Kiki, Biz, Tropo, Gold-Rilla, King Blackbored, and BBA as they all try to help a blacked-out Biz retrace his steps from the previous nightâ€™s adventures.
